asset.hookText:
Hi Cynthia, I read your comment on Amazon.com and have a good idea of what's going on with your Air Steerable. For best pick up performance on floors, always make sure that your vacuum is set for floor mode. I put together this quick video for you to show you how to change the mode settings. Let me know if you need any more help. I'm always here for you. 

-Wil
